# G3 - Out of the Abyss - Into The Darkness 1

## Destinations
* North – to Menzoberranzan (26 days) or Blingdenstone (30 days)
* West – to Sloobludop/Darklake (8 days)
    * Beyond to Blingdenstone (+20 days)
    * Beyond to Gracklstugh (+20 days)
    * Beyond to Neverlight Grove (+26 days)
* South – to Gracklstugh (28 days)
    * Beyond to Neverlight Grove (36 days, can avoid Gracklstugh)


## Where should we go?
* **Buppido** – Gracksltugh - get better equipment and it’s where he is from, but can go there from Darklake as well
* **Prince Derendil** – no idea where he is, wishes to return to surface to lift the curse
* **Eldeth Feldrun** – no idea where she is, but can help with navigation, a tunnel is  a tunnel
* **Jimjar** – Blingdenstone, the svirfneblin city to give access to the surface
* **Sarith Kzekarit** – Darklake to Neverlight Grove to take Stool home (8+26 days)
* **Shuushar** – Darklake and Sloobludop, can navigate to Darklake w/in 3 miles. Sloobludop is a kuo-toa town, *can acquire boats to cross the lake*
* **Stool** – no idea where he is, wants to return to Neverlight Grove. *My people will be grateful and provide you with food, shelter and aid. Also they will probably know how to get to the surface*
* **Topsy and Turvy** – have no suggestion, will go anywhere want to avoid Blingdenstone (they will probably leave)

## To `________` we go
* Refer to Daily Checklist
* Explain to Players
    * Pace
    * Marching Order (get single and two abreast order)
    * Illumination
    * Navigation (who is navigating?)
    * Mapping (who is making a map?)
    * Foraging
* Random Encounters Tables refer to p25

**Additional resting triggers additional encounter roll**

